{"tid":2101622,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"｜消息：沙田水泉澳邨再有確診個案　多人送不同醫院","createTime":"2020-07-10T02:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T05:05:18.000Z","uid":5195,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cb4f1d8f0a9ad204f82e7eebed7bc82d42b0c086","tid":2101622,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:50:49.000Z","msg":"【10:32】綜合多個消息指，早前66歲確診女子居住的水泉澳邨明泉樓，再錄得初步確診個案。有消息人士透露，明泉樓有多宗初步確診，分別送往不同醫院。<br />\n<br />\n而當區區議員丘文俊證實，今天（10日）凌晨有10架救護車把明泉樓初步確診居民送院。他稱，當局周三於該大廈派發深喉唾液樣本瓶，昨天約一半居民交回，該大廈約有500户。據他所知，初步確診個案分散於大廈不同樓層、不同單位。<br />\n<br />\nHk01"},{"pid":"c4d621459df6ddc23cea392c525c1fb59726b1a4","tid":2101622,"uid":14718,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:51:32.000Z","msg":"支那人村"},{"pid":"b2bc2043873763c5f776d33e9693ab3731a5ee7b","tid":2101622,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:53:38.000Z","msg":"哇～又大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6da5b7a6f55875c39bc966b5402cd67edd87118","tid":2101622,"uid":201374,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c4d621459df6ddc23cea392c525c1fb59726b1a4","tid":2101622,"uid":14718,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:51:32.000Z","msg":"支那人村"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:53:48.000Z","msg":"現任區議員為沙田區政成員盧德明。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【光復沙田．3】你所不知道的水泉澳：究竟是「蝗邨」還是「黃邨」？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0-3-%E4%BD%A0%E6%89%80%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E6%B3%89%E6%BE%B3-%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF-%E8%9D%97%E9%82%A8-%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF-%E9%BB%83%E9%82%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0-3-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%2589%2580%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%259F%25A5%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%